A cute look using the new @aboutfacebeauty Better Not Pout Holiday kit ($23USD) 💕

This kit includes two of my favourite About-Face products. The Fractal Glitter Dust Loose Glitters are amazing at taking your makeup look to the next level. It adds so much fun and dimension to your eyes, lips or cheeks. The Cherry Pick Lip Color Butters add so much volume to your lips with great pigmentation. You can shop their holiday kits at aboutface.com
#afpartner #aboutfacebeauty #AD

I love how they feel hydrating and lightweight but they’re also super long-wearing. This lip set is available at @sephora #givenchybeauty AD
